olor": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/649420338"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlqGIxfq97u9dEAMaCTEwNjU5MzI3NiDBrOyvBjAAOB5ABnIJNjQ5NDIwMzM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1711034319.54933", "card_id": "Q_649358301", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "熊猫不走创始人杨振华否认失联传闻，正在寻求解决方案，公司为何会走到这步？还有翻盘的机会吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "3 月 19 日上午，熊猫不走创始人杨振华现身回应失联传闻。此前的 3 月 16 日，「熊猫不走蛋糕」官微发布讨薪信息，称熊猫不走创始人杨振华失联，数千员工三四个月工资未发，社保公积金断缴，老板失联，钉钉群解散，迫于无奈只能网络发声。 根据员工提供给第一财经的一张钉钉群截图，杨振华在 19 日上午召集少数员工进群并对近日传闻作出解释。杨振华称：「我没失联，正在惠州积极配合相关部门了解与处理。也在寻求解决方案。」 杨振华称，目前有三种方案正在推进，一是将区域经营承包给同事甚至供应商，承包者承接欠薪并换取品牌使用权，杨振华认为这个方案本可以成功，但被个别人带歪节奏；二是公司整体出售给同行，目前已有同行接洽；三是融资借贷。熊猫不走创始人杨振华现身：否认失联传闻，解释困局原因"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a9305073dc96e7c219b76bbbcc74f1d8_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "78 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/649358301"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlqGIxfq97u9dEAMaCTEwNjU3OTUwOSDKt+qvBjAAODtAB3IJNjQ5MzU4MzAxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1711034319.56375", "card_id": "Q_648954282", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 51}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些一眼惊艳的八字古诗词？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d823b95b54eab17928bbd01ca185214c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {